      • getCompletions

        void getCompletions(java.lang.String sText,
                    EditorPosition rCaretPosition,
                    int nCaretIndex,
                    AutoCompletionCallback rCallback)
        Called to get the completions for the specified editor text.
        Parameters:
        sText - The text. Not null.
        rCaretPosition - The caret position, containing line and column information. Not null.
        nCaretIndex - The caret index with respect to the editor text. Not null.
        rCallback - A callback that should be used to signal that auto-completion results are ready. Not null.
